    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are mechanically sound and the car runs reliably, there are noticeable signs of wear and tear, including some minor exterior scratches and thinning upholstery in the interior. It has been maintained regularly to ensure safety and functionality, but it is priced to reflect its age and cosmetic imperfections. This is a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
